author: News Tribune
title: Club Basketball: Knights to hold tryouts, camps
text:
Share 
The Knights basketball program is holding tryouts for fifth through eighth-grade boys Oct. 26-28 at Rackers Fieldhouse in Jefferson City. 
The tryouts will be part of a camp for fourth-eighth grade boys. The fourth and fifth grade camp will run from 5:30 p.m.-7 p.m. The sixth and seventh grade camp will run from 7 p.m.-8:30 p.m. The eighth graders will take the court from 8:30 p.m.-9:30 p.m. 
For more information, visit www.knights-basketball.com . ï»¿
